          • <code>shape</code> - visual form (triangle, star, etc.)<br>
          • <code>color</code> - hex color code<br>
          • <code>pos</code> - (x, y) position<br>
          • <code>ai</code> - behavior (idle, wander, chase, flee)<br><br>
