          3. Displays it in the Scene view<br><br>
          <strong>The image IS your game.</strong> Save it, share it, load it anywhere.
        `,
        target: '#btn-compile',
        position: 'bottom'
      },
      {
        title: '🖼️ Step 3: Scene View',
        content: `
